title: Global Tribe Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Raw, Western, Take-out, British, English
description: A vibrant vegetarian cafe located above a crystal shop and has a separate entrance. Has vegan, gluten-free, and raw food including vegan raw cakes. Some dishes can be made vegan on request. Dairy milk and spread used but customers are always asked for their preference.
